{
  "texts": [
    "• MCTest (Richardson et al, 2013).",
    "The MCTest dataset necessitates models to respond to multiple-choice questions related to imaginary narratives.",
    "Given the entirely fictional nature of the text, there is a scarcity of included world knowledge.",
    "The primary focus lies on evaluating the models' proficiency in understanding story content and extracting relevant answers.",
    "• MultiRC (Khashabi et al, 2018)."
  ]
}